+# GitHub controlled-publication contract — 0276-r2
+
+An approved local review, durable SQL/final refs, review and policy decisions,
+expected remote revision and explicit operator flags are mandatory inputs.
+
+The pure planner supports issue comments, issue body updates and label
+replacement. It adds a deterministic marker to text mutations and produces a
+payload compatible with the existing default-closed remote mutation gate.
+
+No HTTP call occurs. Every plan declares that a 0276-r4 collision guard is
+required before apply.
