+# Changelog — 0276-r2 GitHub controlled-publication contract
+
+## Added
+
+- added a pure publication command and plan;
+- required approved review, durable refs and expected remote revision;
+- produced an existing-gate-compatible dry-run payload.
+
+## Boundaries
+
+- one existing Scheduler only;
+- SQL remains durable authority;
+- GitHub mutation remains closed unless this phase explicitly reaches the guarded adapter;
+- no secret is serialized.
